# MGR cross-tool handoff (Cursor ↔ Claude Code)

Global guide: `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` · Per-repo: `.clauderules` · Detail: `docs/HANDOFF.md`

## On resume (`/go`)

1. **`MGR/sessions/handoff.md`** — read first
2. **`MGR/tasks.json`** — each pending task needs `context` (doing, achieve, according); see `docs/TASK_CONTEXT.md`
3. **`MGR/sessions/worklog.md`** (tail) — `docs/WORKLOG.md`
4. **`MGR/sessions/latest.md`** (tail)
5. **`.mgr/memory/MEMORY.md`**

## Task worklog (required)

On every **create / start / complete / reopen / edit / delete** in `MGR/tasks.json`, append one block to **`MGR/sessions/worklog.md`** immediately (do not wait for `/stop`). mgr app logs automatically on save.

## Before leaving (`/stop`)

1. **Overwrite** `MGR/sessions/handoff.md` (`tool: cursor`)
2. **Append** to `MGR/sessions/latest.md` (session summary; reference task ids)
3. Update **`MGR/tasks.json`** — pending tasks require `context` blurbs; worklog any task changes from this session
4. Reply: **Handoff saved.**
